# 🎓 Udemey - Udemy Clone

A pixel-perfect frontend clone of **Udemy**, the popular online 
learning platform. Built from scratch using pure HTML, CSS, and 
Font Awesome icons.

## 🚀 Live Demo
👉 [Click here to view](https://nitro77-gx.github.io/Udemy-clone/)

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3 (Flexbox, Animations, Media Queries)
- Font Awesome Icons
- Google Fonts (Gabarito)

## ✨ Features
- 📌 Sticky Navigation Bar with search input
- 🗂️ Category pills with 3D hover animation
- 🖼️ Hero banner with slide-in card animation
- 📚 Recommended Courses section with course cards
- 🏷️ Topics section (Web Dev, React JS, AWS, Docker & more)
- 🔥 Most Popular Courses section
- 🛒 My Learning dropdown on hover
- 📱 Fully Responsive (Mobile & Tablet friendly)
- 🦶 Footer with links and copyright

